==History==
mymensingh zilla school established in 1847 not in 1853

==Admission==
Generally, admission is permitted in class three and six once in a year. There is no eligibility for admission test, and with good performance in admission test, students are usually admitted in these two classes. However, sometimes outstanding students could be easily get admitted in class nine from any other school. Though, there is still no breach in admission system, preference may be given request comes from any teacher from this school.
===Tuition fee===
Due to be a government school, tuition fee is very low compared to private school. Tuition fee also includes tiffin fee and it is usually taken monthly basis. There are three fixed dates when tuition fee is taken and first two dates are penalty less. In each class, there are 2/3 class representative who usually deal with teachers and take care of tiffin. Class representatives are elected by the class with a guidance of the class teacher.

==School uniform==
* Full sleeve white shirt in winter and half sleeve in summer
* Brown color pants
* White socks and shoes

